{"tid":12564,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[推算] 以「高登指數」推算LIHKG 令高登少左幾多人","createTime":"2016-11-29T17:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T08:21:55.000Z","uid":2861,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dda4913289bb17284aefcf97bb0b56df094e6d6","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"手機開post 唔cap 圖影mon 算<br />\n拿高登有一樣野 叫高登指數 每個ac 只可以投票一次，應該冇咩人知 因為網頁版係公告旁邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/004102_0df27c0c70ebbf757d9e035d55081dee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F004102_0df27c0c70ebbf757d9e035d55081dee.jpg&h=e23b3159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以見到右上角係有過往記錄 㩒入去睇睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/004143_f8ae2b92c62fb667a7de86e3b6a11d10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F004143_f8ae2b92c62fb667a7de86e3b6a11d10.jpg&h=fbee13e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLihkg 開左之後 明顯係少左人投票 一於計計少左幾多人，問題係幾多人呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/004355_4906475d0410b5748e0a2a6d8fb8072e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F004355_4906475d0410b5748e0a2a6d8fb8072e.jpg&h=63f39f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nF5左好多次 我知左面個數係假 但右面既163160係冇變過，根據香港網絡大典，高登每月瀏覽人次係三十七萬 除以31日 每日11935人 但係網典既Alexa 香港排名同埋高登歷史版本都只係記載至2013年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0xfAq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0xfAq4.jpg&h=99a21b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/005008_cb1a728bf58929ad41558c39c3c7746e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F005008_cb1a728bf58929ad41558c39c3c7746e.jpg&h=1460c3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮呢幾年既增長 先信住2016年高登仔共163160人</span><br />\n<br />\n然後計算過去高登指數平均投票數字 因為唔係個個議題都有興趣投（雖然佢有唔關我事呢個選擇） <br />\n<br />\n先唔計最新個次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2035U9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2035U9J.jpg&h=47073fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平均數係353人左右<br />\n<br />\n353-201(lihkg開壇後高登指數）= 152<br />\n152除以353= 0.430959<br />\n<br />\n<strong>即係lihkg 開壇後 高登指數少左43%人參加投票</strong><br />\n<br />\n163160(高登仔人數） x 43.0959% =70256(取整數）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推數結果：lihkg 開壇後高登立即少左七萬人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以上就估住咁多先 數字唔一定精準 但少左呢堆人係連高登指數都玩埋既高登仔 咁唔知呢樣既野人黎？<br />\n<br />\n信不信由你<br />\n利申文科撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3d97205627a318cdab490548be7cfb807bd71e","tid":12564,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"TLDR"},{"pid":"8b4e089ea7ac2421d66bbb4057dbbeaa42b8854c","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TLDR</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6a0c212744942b8a7f797ec15d800f9cb10ba3","tid":12564,"uid":13396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好既開始"},{"pid":"0ebdff4b4ed36a06847ef068d74dd73a90e5f20c","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好既開始</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日上真係有當初一開始上高登既感覺 大家加油"},{"pid":"c09b7de6c795990704afd1337e49e37230206a28","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:15:31.000Z","msg":"十六萬人走七萬 都成一半  我希望真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但201真係咁耐高登指數既新低"},{"pid":"d15794ad22adce9bf619bc4b1e412720ab0231db","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/12558/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/12558/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個post 巴打得出高登帖文流失左一半"},{"pid":"080bd963bab644f32788e4b55d0900ac99c9692a","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da5e7f456331b130f81bf50a1479c9176508a2c","tid":12564,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:25:30.000Z","msg":"7 萬active user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9536119ae2c43e2c69a76582b903f582810c2796","tid":12564,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:26:50.000Z","msg":"數據有理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af74b7c79f460159864453d2b6967066d6fc9ab3","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數據有理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c8e29bdbcff7371a134e771247879abed1e96b","tid":12564,"uid":25278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"323cd33b24228d8a6f92e14b415e0b8fb7e7a726","tid":12564,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"好專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e927622d4333e3691ed5db879ae4c9ae70c0c1fb","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7 萬active user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連高登指數都玩埋 真係擁躉黎 都走埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353638798c74313dcf1bbf89bbf8a0a87b4e5dff","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咩 多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a93410657713d1e86833162585b5b361808a21f","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8693cfdd51b7eb9e4278a92bbe20ad22df5c37be","tid":12564,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"有fd crawl 高登post量，只係出左ios版都少左一半，出左an版應該仲少"},{"pid":"59ccf79f323383a679544bafc577dc94e1661bb4","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有fd crawl 高登post量，只係出左ios版都少左一半，出左an版應該仲少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢最新個投票由23號開始有得投 lihkg 開壇前兩日 所以已經係樂觀估計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f782204ab52f993691b0a6fa2e0c395c8f0178e","tid":12564,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"用高登指數推算我覺得唔準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一來依個功能係網頁版專用, 所以平時用開HKG+或者lihk甚至dat都甚少會參與<br />\n況且投票又唔係點名, 就算仲上緊高登都可以一時投一時唔投<br />\n<br />\n我記得之前有個post係計每日回覆量, 嗰個做指標應該準好多"},{"pid":"64618fdefcc07bc046119be6ac17e9b9b3def29c","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用高登指數推算我覺得唔準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一來依個功能係網頁版專用, 所以平時用開HKG+或者lihk甚至dat都甚少會參與<br />\n況且投票又唔係點名, 就算仲上緊高登都可以一時投一時唔投<br />\n<br />\n我記得之前有個post係計每日回覆量, 嗰個做指標應該準好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩search 過 del 左post<br />\n呢個數字唔反映緊既係網頁版既活躍會員都過檔既數字<br />\n至於一時投一時唔投呢個問題我用左平均數黎計希望少d 誤差"},{"pid":"9878628376f4d70792e6321b360a41ac4611d3de","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3f0c1c552beb314180201e03329c2bc35ae7b2","tid":12564,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f97ede2be385a4962049d46e7579daba8d32de","tid":12564,"uid":31528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用高登指數推算我覺得唔準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一來依個功能係網頁版專用, 所以平時用開HKG+或者lihk甚至dat都甚少會參與<br />\n況且投票又唔係點名, 就算仲上緊高登都可以一時投一時唔投<br />\n<br />\n我記得之前有個post係計每日回覆量, 嗰個做指標應該準好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打講得啱喎，個投票指數本身就有bias<br />\n投得係本身用電腦上開又無聊嘅人先會投<br />\n所以應該唔準確<br />\n但係樂見高登冇人上"},{"pid":"03f0c28cd068219703b9fecf241b220cbd34c8d6","tid":12564,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:49:36.000Z","msg":"等Alexa出LIHKG排名好過啦 最準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80959f4adea63488856b4af06d7d9c6c67df5bd0","tid":12564,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"啱啱我講個post喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[革命即將成功] LiHKG VS 高登 ， 開Post數量統計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/11558/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/11558/page/1?ref=ios</a>"}]}